# ğŸ¦ Bank System - Phase 1

A comprehensive banking system developed in C++ with Object-Oriented Programming principles.

## ğŸ“‹ Project Overview

This is **Phase 1** of a multi-phase banking system project. It implements the core classes and validation logic for managing clients, employees, and administrators.

## âœ¨ Features

### Client Management
- âœ… Create client accounts with validation
- âœ… Deposit money
- âœ… Withdraw money (with minimum balance enforcement)
- âœ… Transfer money between clients
- âœ… Check account balance
- âœ… Display client information

### Employee Management
- âœ… Create employee accounts
- âœ… Salary management (minimum 5000 EGP)
- âœ… Display employee information

### Admin Management
- âœ… Inherits all employee features
- âœ… Additional administrative privileges (to be implemented in Phase 2)

### Validation System
- âœ… Name validation (alphabetic, 3-20 characters)
- âœ… Password validation (8-20 characters, no spaces)
- âœ… Balance validation (minimum 1500 EGP)
- âœ… Salary validation (minimum 5000 EGP)

