## ğŸ“Š Validation Rules

| Field | Rule |
|-------|------|
| Name | Alphabetic characters only, 3-20 characters |
| Password | 8-20 characters, no spaces |
| Client Balance | Minimum 1500 EGP |
| Employee/Admin Salary | Minimum 5000 EGP |

